# Frontend agent (FE lane)

## Scope

- **Only** edit files under `frontend/`.
- Do not change `backend/`, `ai-service/`, or `docs/` unless user asks.

## Stack

- React 18 + TypeScript + Vite + Ant Design + Tailwind + Recharts
- Entry: `frontend/src/App.tsx` (monolith; prefer new `src/services/`, `src/hooks/` over growing App.tsx when adding API)

## Data rules

- Mock state today: `productsList`, `invoicesList`, `importSlips`, `posCart`, `activePromotions`, `chatHistory`
- When wiring APIs: map BE DTOs — do not assume `Product.key` === BE `UUID`; use explicit mappers
- Concept diagram: `frontend/react.MD`

## API client

- Base URL: `VITE_API_URL` trong `frontend/.env.local` (đọc qua `@/lib/env` → `API_BASE_URL`, default `http://localhost:8080`)
- Parse `ApiResponse<T>`: `{ success, message, data }`
- Attach JWT from storage on every request after login

## UI conventions

- Vietnamese labels for user-facing copy (match existing screens)
- Reuse `frontend/src/components/ui.tsx` (`Card`, `UiButton`, `StatusChip`)
- Use `cn()` from `frontend/src/lib/utils.ts`

## Out of scope for FE agent

- JPA entities, Flyway, Kafka, Gemini server calls, Python ML training
